         <abstract id="aspace_e14a3e1a5bdf4d1790dd9433a14464a7">This collection, compiled by William H. Brown, contains a variety of financial documents concerning coal mining companies operating in the North American West. Examples of these documents include letters to the stock- and bondholders, mortgage indentures, prospectuses, and subscription agreements. While all of these documents are represented in the collection, they are not all represented by each company.</abstract>
